    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Fair-condition car being sold as an honest driver with typical wear for its age and use. It runs and drives, but it is not a perfect vehicle and should be expected to show noticeable cosmetic blemishes, interior wear, and some signs of age throughout. It appears suitable for someone looking for basic transportation or a budget-friendly vehicle, but buyers should expect some deferred maintenance and minor repairs may be needed over time. Overall, this is a decent, usable car for someone who understands they are buying a fair-condition vehicle rather than a pristine example.",
