      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and wear, but for the right buyer it represents a practical opportunity for commuting, a first car, or a project. Priced with transparency and value in mind, this is an economical way to get on the road without overspending.",
