    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable runabout with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, drives, and offers a great opportunity for someone who wants dependable basic transport without spending a fortune. Ideal as a first car, spare vehicle, or a handy project for someone who enjoys tinkering. Priced fairly and described honestly \u2014 if you want a straightforward deal from a seller who believes in being upfront, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with a willing powertrain, smooth-shifting drivetrain, and solid road manners. This is not a showroom piece, but it has the bones enthusiasts look for: responsive throttle, composed chassis feel, and the kind of mechanical honesty that makes it a great budget driver, commuter, or starter project. Recent upkeep and usable condition make it an appealing way into ownership without breaking the bank. Priced to move and well-suited for someone who appreciates a straightforward, serviceable car with real potential.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
