      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with honest character and plenty of story left to tell, this ride has the kind of presence that makes every trip feel a little more memorable. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone who appreciates value, enjoys bringing out a vehicle\u2019s next chapter, or just wants an inexpensive set of wheels with personality. There\u2019s a rugged charm here that stands out from cookie-cutter commuters, and for the right buyer, it\u2019s a chance to get into something with real spirit at a very approachable price.",
